{"ts":"2026-07-06T08:03:07.959Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/446\n\n## Problem\n`pm get` omits the schedule facet (events/start_at/end_at/location) for Meeting/Event/Reminder items — the single-item read primitive cannot show the defining fields of calendar types; agents must fall back to calendar/agenda commands.\n\n## Proposed fix\nInclude the schedule facet in pm get output (standard depth and above; respect --fields), matching where list/agenda expose it.\n\n## Definition of done\npm get shows events/start_at/end_at/location for scheduled types in TOON and JSON; spec added; docs COMMANDS.md get section updated."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-x1g5"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-446: pm get omits schedule facet (events/start_at/end_at/location) for Meeting/Event/Reminder"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood GH-446: the single-item read primitive hides the defining fields of calendar types. Duplicate check: searched get schedule meeting event — pm-uzmf (closed calendar ergonomics) did not cover get projection; no open overlap."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["area:cli","bug","calendar","gh-issue"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:07.959Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:07.959Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":60},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"pm get renders the schedule facet for scheduled types in TOON and JSON at standard depth; --fields can project it; spec + COMMANDS.md updated"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"196b4af47be240c1bb299d15b4f8b5f370c3a1246a3cf742e47338f0d8291efc","message":""}
